A.5. How to Ask Questions 544
A.4.2 UCI Machine Learning Repository
The University of California at Irvine hosts a large number of free machine learning datasets,
including many for time series forecasting and time series classiﬁcation. Some examples of time
series datasets on the UCI repository include:
 EEG Eye State Dataset.
http://archive.ics.uci.edu/ml/datasets/EEG+Eye+State
 Room Occupancy Detection Dataset.
http://archive.ics.uci.edu/ml/datasets/Occupancy+Detection+
